T. S. SALATHIEL v. WESTERN SERVICE CORPORATION et al. No. 1196. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. March 25, 1935. T. S. Salathiel, of Independence, Kan., for appellant. Rainey, Flynn, Green & Anderson, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellees.

Before LEWIS and McDERMOTT, Circuit Judges, and KENNEDY, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on stipulation.
